{\pard\plain \qj \fi-2160\li2160\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx540\tx720\tx1440\faroman\rin0\lin2160\itap0\pararsid988924 \b\v\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid988924 {\tc {\b\fs24\insrsid988924 
System Analysis for a multi-tier, DII-COE system (2001) \tcl4}}}{\b\fs24\insrsid988924 
\par }\pard\plain \s24\ql \li936\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\faroman\rin0\lin936\itap0\pararsid988924 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid988924 Developed J2EE application (JBoss}{\insrsid8007445 /Jetty}{\insrsid988924 ) using JS
P, Servlets, and EJB to allow an organization to build a community library of original documents (MS-Word}{\insrsid8007445 , text,}{\insrsid988924  and HTML), abstracts, and other references.  The library
 allows custom categories, full text searching, and document browsing.  Document access and submission is controlled by the administrator via user roles.  Users register themselves but must respond to a server generated e-mail validation request.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi-2160\li2160\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx540\tx720\tx1440\faroman\rin0\lin2160\itap0\pararsid988924 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs24\insrsid988924 \tab }{\b\fs24\insrsid988924 Data distribution and 
collection application with WinCE/PocketPC client (2002) }{\pard\plain \qj \fi-2160\li2160\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx540\tx720\tx1440\faroman\rin0\lin2160\itap0\pararsid988924 
\b\v\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid988924 {\tc {\b\fs24\insrsid988924 System Analysis for a multi-tier, DII-COE system (2001) \tcl4}}}{\b\fs24\insrsid988924 
\par }\pard\plain \s24\ql \li936\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\faroman\rin0\lin936\itap0\pararsid988924 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid988924 Developed data distribution and collection application that allows a non-programmer 
to generate custom forms and wizards for use on a handheld client.  The administrator may then distribute selected subsets of data from the database (in XML format) to multiple handheld clients and allow database updates (automatically or with selective 
approval of the administrator) after the client uploads the modified dataset.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi-2160\li2160\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx540\tx720\tx1440\faroman\rin0\lin2160\itap0\pararsid5270591 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs24\insrsid5270591 \tab }{\b\fs24\insrsid5270591 
System Analysis for a multi-tier, DII-COE system (2001) }{\pard\plain \qj \fi-2160\li2160\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx540\tx720\tx1440\faroman\rin0\lin2160\itap0\pararsid5270591 
\b\v\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5270591 {\tc {\b\fs24\insrsid5270591 System Analysis for a multi-tier, DII-COE system (2001) \tcl4}}}{\b\fs24\insrsid5270591 
