 multi-tier, distributed component system.  A CORBA interface was added to an existing Win32 application (Delphi) to use it as a server component in this EJB system. 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \li540\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\faroman\rin0\lin540\itap0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\pard\plain \qj \li540\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\faroman\rin0\lin540\itap0 
