\par }\pard\plain \s24\ql \li936\ri0\sl360\slmult0\nowidctlpar\faroman\rin0\lin936\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid8007445 System architect and developer of this peer to peer system.  UTC\_
DT automates the generation of equipment requirements based on user defined rules and enables individuals to tailor those requirements.  It uses a custom peer\_to\_
peer socket communication protocol developed for this project to allow multiple users across a LAN or the Internet to efficiently view and update the same detailed information.
